title: Undekhi
overview: Show depicts the two aspects of the society - the power-drunk influential people who think they can get away with anything and the oppressed, subjected to years of torture, who finally decide to bring themselves to justice

tv.episodeTitle: Catch The Tiger By The Tail
tv.episodeOverview: Rishi, Koyal, and Praful give Ghosh and the others a tough chase as they track them in the jungle. Saloni tells Teji about the murder and their predicament. Rinku lays a trap for Rishi and pins murder on him.
